minicom

Launch:
	sudo minicom

Attach a different device
    sudo minicom --device </path/to/device>
    sudo minicom --device /dev/ttyUSB0

For example, to find a USB device:
#Display names of all usb devices
lsusb

#Devices are located in /dev as ttyUSB<n>
ls /dev/tty*
    or
ls /dev/ttyUSB*

Help:
	^A Z
